snippet.title: Warden of the Coast - Launch Trailer | 2022 Skyrim Mod
snippet.description:
It's almost here! Warden of the Coast will officially launch on the 2nd of December, 2022.

Warden of the Coast will release for PC on Skyrim Special Edition. An Xbox version is possible but not currently in the works. No PS4 version can be released due to Sony's policy on mod assets.

Trailer Credits:

Voice over work by the incredible Daniel Berry
https://www.castingcall.club/DBerry_VO

Voice of Dagon by the amazing Schoootly
https://www.castingcall.club/schoootly

First two tracks are by the talented Scott Buckley
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1skC53i8FBc
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qYTJ8hDj_Hc

Final track is from the Skyrim Soundtrack
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6fILxnBH1Tg

Editing by yours truly.
